#

Hearty Vegetable Soup

45 min
$10
250 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianLow FatGluten Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main

Tags:

SoupComfort FoodEasyHealthy

Description

A comforting and nutritious soup packed with seasonal vegetables and beans, perfect for a cozy meal.

Ingredients

  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • carrots: 2, diced
  • celery: 2 stalks, diced
  • onion: 1, chopped
  • garlic: 3 cloves, minced
  • canned diced tomatoes: 1 can (14.5 oz)
  • vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • green beans: 1 cup, chopped
  • zucchini: 1, diced
  • canned white beans: 1 can (15 oz), drained and rinsed
  • spinach: 2 cups, fresh
  • bay leaf: 1
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • italian seasoning: 1 teaspoon
